<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: despised -->
  <VRE_Androids_Despised.label>厌恶</VRE_Androids_Despised.label>
  <!-- EN: Androids are inferior to humans. I harbor disdain and contempt for them, as I believe they disrupt the natural order and threaten our humanity. -->
  <VRE_Androids_Despised.description>人形永远也无法与人类相提并论。他们是扰乱自然规律与践踏人性的可憎之物，我们绝不容许他们的存在。</VRE_Androids_Despised.description>
  <!-- EN: Android -->
  <VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.0.description>人形</VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.0.description>
  <!-- EN: Android self hatred -->
  <VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.2.description>人形自怨</VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.2.description>
  <!-- EN: Android among us -->
  <VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.3.description>殖民地有人形</VRE_Androids_Despised.comps.3.description>
  
  <!-- EN: equal -->
  <VRE_Androids_Equal.label>平等</VRE_Androids_Equal.label>
  <!-- EN: We firmly stand for android equality, asserting that androids have the same rights, opportunities, and moral consideration as their human counterparts. -->
  <VRE_Androids_Equal.description>人形理应享有与人类同等的权力、机会与地位，我们需要为他们施予道德关怀。</VRE_Androids_Equal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: respected -->
  <VRE_Androids_Respected.label>重视</VRE_Androids_Respected.label>
  <!-- EN: Androids' sophisticated technology and intelligence should be acknowledged. We should treat them with admiration and esteem, even if they are different from humans. -->
  <VRE_Androids_Respected.description>人形先进的技术与智能应当得到人类的认可。尽管人形与人类之间存在差异，但我们仍该尊重并敬佩他们。</VRE_Androids_Respected.description>
  <!-- EN: Android -->
  <VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.0.description>人形</VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.0.description>
  <!-- EN: No androids -->
  <VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.1.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>非人形</VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.1.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>
  <!-- EN: Androids in colony (+1 per each android, up to +10) -->
  <VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.1.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>殖民地有人形（每个人形提供1点心情增益，上限为10点）</VRE_Androids_Respected.comps.1.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>
  
  <!-- EN: tools -->
  <VRE_Androids_Tools.label>工具</VRE_Androids_Tools.label>
  <!-- EN: We view androids as mere tools, designed to serve and assist humans in various tasks, asserting that they exist solely for our convenience and should not be attributed with any rights or moral consideration.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color>\n - No opinion generation of Androids.\n - No thoughts related to androids dying (works for all colonists as long as precept is part of primary ideology).\n - No thoughts related to androids being enslaved (works for all colonists as long as precept is part of primary ideology). -->
  <VRE_Androids_Tools.description>人形仅仅是用来取悦并辅助人类的工具罢了，他们不配拥有任何权力与地位。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;游戏效果：&lt;/color&gt;\n - 人类殖民者不会对人形产生任何评价和看法。\n - 所有殖民者都不会在乎人形是否死亡（当前主流文化形态拥有此戒律时，将对所有殖民者生效）。\n - 所有殖民者都不会在乎人形是否被奴役（当前主流文化形态拥有此戒律时，将对所有殖民者生效）。</VRE_Androids_Tools.description>
  
</LanguageData>